				  Necrow NeCrow
			   Paid'o' File'o' File


  An Arcadish game powered by the Ogre3D rendering engine,
we made it available for both Microsoft(R.) Windows(T.M.) 
and GNU(?) Linux(?) operating systems ...maybe you could 
emulate it on Apple Makintosh or something else for free?!
We probably do hope so.

It will not be available for mobile phones because we believe
the usually small screens are not enough to appreciate the game.

It will not be available to Android because we believe
they are probably already dreaming about electric chips or 
tortillaz possibly.

The game is available for free or for a fee, suggested
price is $1 (unit).

Brought to you by L.C.W.E.
